	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">把发布会变成脱口秀后，韩寒公布了新片《三重门》</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-14 16:12:54 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">6</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">20</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/25466.html" class="com-grid-article" >
